'''Jo da Silva''', numukinyi wamafirime  muri Afrika yepfo n'umunyamakuru kuri tereviziyo. Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri serial zizwi cyane ''Gabriël'', ''Operation Delta Force 3: Clear Target'' na ''Arsenaal'' . <ref name="joda">https://sarafinamagazine.com/2018/02/28/a-conversation-with-jo-da-silva/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Da Silva yarangije muri kaminuza ya Wits mu 1990 afite impamyabumenyi y'icyubahiro mu buhanzi bw'ikinamico. <ref name="motivator">https://www.motivators.co.za/jo-da-silva/</ref> Afite kandi impamyabumenyi ya mwarimu mu myigire yimikino. <ref name="motivator" />

Da Silva yashakanye n'umukinnyi wa [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo Eckard Rabe kuva 1996 kugeza 2007. <ref name="dead">https://www.news24.com/you/archive/back-from-the-dead-20170728-4</ref> Abashakanye bafite umukobwa umwe, Caitlin. <ref name="dead" /> Muri 2010, Da Silva na Rabe bombi bagize uruhare mu isabune yo muri Afrika yepfo, ''7de Laan.'' <ref name="dead" />

== Umwuga ==
Da Silva yatangiye umwuga we mu ikinamico kandi akomeza imyaka myinshi mu ikinamico. Yagaragaye muri sabune opera ''Isidingo'' akina nka 'Natasha Wallace'.

Hanyuma yakinnye nka 'Gita McGregor' kuri televiziyo ''7de Laan'' . <ref>https://esat.sun.ac.za/index.php/Jo_da_Silva</ref> Ku mirimo ye nka Gita McGregor, Da Silva yatowe mu cyiciro cya "Umugore w’umugore w’indashyikirwa" mu birori byo gutangiza ibihembo bya Royalty Soapie mu 2013. <ref name="inaugural">https://www.news24.com/you/archive/inaugural-royalty-soapie-awards-20170728</ref> Muri 2015, yatorewe igihembo cya Royalty Soapie Award mu cyiciro cya "Umugore w’umugore w’indashyikirwa" kubera uruhare rwe kuri ''7de Laan.'' <ref name="royalty2015">https://www.news24.com/channel/the-juice/royalty-soapie-awards-nominees-revealed-20150330</ref> Da Silva kandi yatowe mu cyiciro cya "Umukinnyi mwiza w'isabune nziza" kubera ibikorwa yakoze kuri ''7de Laan'' muri 2016 ''Huisgenoot'' <ref name="tempo">https://www.news24.com/channel/news/local/these-are-all-the-nominees-for-the-2016-huisgenoot-tempo-awards-20160610</ref> Tempo Awards. Da Silva yavuye muri 7de Laan mu 2016, yimukira i Cape Town kumarana igihe n'umukobwa we no gukora akazi k'ubuntu. <ref name="leaving">https://www.news24.com/channel/tv/news/heres-why-gita-is-leaving-the-laan-20160509</ref>

Usibye izo nshingano, Da Silva yanakinnye kuri televiziyo nyinshi zirimo ''Gabriel'', ''Arsenaal'', ''Madam & Eve'', ''Suburban Bliss'' na ''Egoli'' . Guhera mu 2007, yakinnye nka 'Olivia Fitzgerald' muri televiziyo izwi cyane ya ''Erfsondes'' . <ref>https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=4580</ref>

Nyuma yo kuruhuka igihe kirekire avuye mu ikinamico, amaherezo yagarutse kuri stage akina ibintu bibiri mu ikinamico ''Present Laughter'' rwanditswe na Noël Coward. Ikinamico yerekanwe kuri Theatre ku Kigobe. Hanyuma yakinnye mu ikinamico, ''Fatal Attraction'', yerekanwe kuri Theatre kuri Bay na Pieter Toerien's Monte Casino Theatre i Johannesburg.

Usibye gukina, yanatunganije, afatanya kuyobora ndetse anerekana ikinyamakuru M-Net show 'Showbuzz'. Yabaye kandi umuyobozi wumugore mukinamico yicyongereza,''It rained last night''.. <ref>https://www.motivators.co.za/jo-da-silva/</ref>

